sourcesContent:
<form [formGroup]="onadd" (ngSubmit)="onSubmit()">
    <lable>name</lable>
    <input type="text" formControlName="name">
    <lable>image</lable>
    <input type="text" formControlName="image">
    <lable>url</lable>
    <input type="text" formControlName="ur;">
    <lable>description</lable>
    <input type="text" formControlName="description">
    <lable>view</lable>
    <input type="number" formControlName="view">
    <button type="submit">Add</button>
</form>
